           +----------------------------+---------------------------+
           |                            |                           |
+----------v----------+      +----------v----------+     +----------v----------+
|  Authentication     |      |  Asset Service      |     |  Pricing Service    |
|     Service         |      +----------+----------+     +----------+----------+
+----------+----------+                 |                         |
           |                            |                         |
+----------v----------+   +-------------v------------+    +-------v-------------+
|      User DB        |   |        Asset DB          |    |      Pricing DB     |
+---------------------+   +--------------------------+    +---------------------+
           |                                                      |
